    "Initially, a PdfReader object is created to represent the entire PDF, facilitating seamless interaction with its content [22].",
    "Workflow of the Proposed ModelTo extract the raw text, the model iteratively traverses each page using a loop, employing the extract_text() method.",
    "The extracted texts are then consolidated into a single string variable, pdf_text, which captures the entire textual content of the PDF.",
    "Given the potentially large size of pdf_text, the model implements text chunking to improve computational efficiency.",
